# All optional. The app runs with zero config: in-memory store and built-in stable
# defaults for the JWT secret and RSA transport keypair (so auth + encryption work
# across serverless instances without config). Override the two secrets in prod.
# There is no seeded account — create one via the Register screen.

# JWT_SECRET=<random string>       # overrides the built-in default HS256 secret
# JWT_EXPIRE_MINUTES=10080
# RSA_PRIVATE_KEY=                  # PEM; overrides the built-in transport keypair
# CORS_ORIGINS=https://your-ui.example.com   # only needed if the UI is a separate origin
